Winner For a Beginner!
This beautifully presented family home situated in the highly sought after Highlands Estate will be sure to impress all. Inspections will not disappoint!

Description:
Immaculate House- Blue-Chip Location
Welcome to this massive double storey delight in the heart of extremely sort after Mt. Aitken Estate.
Upon entrance you will be welcomed by open space and wide corridors which has a generous study/lounge leading on to massive rumpus/theatre room. Walk through to the open plan kitchen, with high-class 900mm quality appliances throughout and stone benchtop with waterfall edging which opens up to huge butler's pantry for that extra storage space.
Massive family area is complemented with separate meals/dining space which opens up to landscaped backyard and oversized undercover alfresco area.
Additional 3 bedrooms all with built in robes and accompanied by one big central bathroom.
Easy access to Mt. Aitken Road, Craigieburn Central Shopping precinct, Splash Aqua Park, Pelican Childcare and quality public and private schools in the area along with public transport at your doorstep, this property is centrally located for ease and convenience.
Built with high inclusions and eye for perfection this home will be a prized possession for one lucky buyer. Inspection is must for luxury home buyers with taste for perfection!!

Description:
Lifestyle living at its best!
It's clear from the outset that something very special awaits beyond the captivating facade of this modern, single storey residence. Beautifully positioned in a tranquil setting within the Amberfield Estate, it stands proudly amongst its competitors. Designed with a strong emphasis on natural light and indoor/outdoor living, this superior residence delivers an elegant and truly functional floor plan. From the moment you step inside you will be impressed by its grand entrance. Featuring: A large study 4th bedroom, expansive theatre room, spacious laundry, impressive open plan kitchen, dining, living and rumpus zones with direct access to the covered alfresco with wraparound spacious gardens backing onto the Craigieburn Golf Course. Appointed to quality standards, the high ceilings and modern kitchen incorporating: walk in pantry, stone bench tops with tiled splash back, 900mm freestanding stainless steel stove; all have the wow factor and complements the superb living area, complete with a wood fire heater, making it the ultimate entertainer. The master bedroom will be your own private oasis featuring a large walk in robe, full luxury ensuite featuring double vanities on a beautifully crafted floating vanity unit including large shower and separate toilet. Sleek central bathroom appointed to matching luxury services the rest of the home's large bedrooms that feature triple sliding door robes.Well designed and impeccably presented, this residence also comes with:
Remote double car garage with internal access
Gated side access, ideal for boats, caravans or work vehicles
Wood fire place to main living
Ducted heating and refrigerated cooling
Alarm system
Timber look floors
Large alfresco with extended decking area
12 Solar panels
3 phase power
Water point to fridge
House built on brick piers with concrete footings
And much, much more...
Offering easy access and a short distance to Public Transport, many parks, multiple Shopping Centres, high Educational Schools, Medical Centres, Sport Fields, Splash Aquatic centre and much more that Craigieburn has to offer. This exceptional property is ready to respond effortlessly to modern family requirements with relaxed sophistication and style.

Description:
Family Flexibility with Parkside Perfection!
Occupying an exceptionally wide elevated allotment overlooking the green expanse of Hamilton Hume Reserve, this distinctive double-storey 4BR home assures a fine family lifestyle with its indoor versatility and impressive outdoor space.
Beyond its attractive rendered facade, the home's impeccably-presented interior boasts a large master bedroom with WIR, private ensuite and park views, along with 3 additional bedrooms (one downstairs), main family bathroom and guest powder room (third WC).
Adding to its appeal are 3 distinct living zones including a light-filled lounge, rumpus/retreat (upstairs) and open family/dining area as well as an adjoining kitchen complete with walk-in pantry, stainless steel cooking appliances and dishwasher.
Other stand-out features of the home include ducted heating and split-system air conditioning (both levels), ceiling fans to all bedrooms, large laundry, plus a huge backyard with entertaining area, lush lawn, established perimeter gardens for added privacy as well as a remote-control double garage with storage area and drive-through option.
In a popular family-focused neighbourhood, it's also close to Grand Boulevard buses, local shops, childcare centre and primary schools, as well as easy access to Craigieburn's major shopping centres and the Hume Freeway.

Description:
Turn Over A New Leaf
Small changes can reap huge rewards in this thoughtfully designed three bedroom home with an enormous open living/dining/kitchen, large easily maintained outdoor space and northerly rear aspect. Nestled in a bend in the road, effectively resulting in a corner position, it offers high ceilings and abundant windows, maximising the sense of space and natural light. There's a wealth of room for the lounge suite and dining table, and the kitchen comes with a gas cooktop, fan forced oven, dishwasher, pantry and abundant bench space. The main bedroom leads past built-in robes to the dual entry bathroom, in a central position, plus there's a convenient separate toilet and laundry. Heating and cooling are in place to boost comfort, there's a driveway and carport, and the residence presents the opportunity to easily enhance and really make it your own. A short stroll to The Greenway Reserve and buses to Craigieburn Station and Craigieburn Central, it's also close to several schools and Craigieburn Golf Course.

Description:
PERFECT HOME ON A PERFECT BLOCK APPROX. 739m2!!!
Here is a wonderful opportunity to purchase this completely renovated home on a massive 739m2 of land. Step inside and instantly embrace the style and fantastic finishes.
This 3-bedroom home, all with BIRs, is sure to impress. Comprising of a contemporary country style kitchen- which is only 4 years old with 600mm white fisher & paykel appliances, gorgeous double sink and brass fittings & timber bench tops , a glorious bathroom with floor to ceiling tiles & a timeless free standing cast iron bath tub that will help you to relax and recharge, open plan living with floorboards throughout and new carpets to all bedrooms, and a study nestled at the rear of the home. As you ponder and look outside, you will be lost in your thoughts. French doors open out to a decked entertaining area, surrounded by picturesque beauty. Your eyes take you beyond the boundaries, to a place of solitude and peace. Also has the potential to build a unit at the back STCA.
Further inclusions:
Drop ceiling pendants in kitchen
Feature fire place and mantel
Timber floors
Split system cooling
Ducted heating + gas and electronic heater
White timber curtains
LED lights throughout the whole house
Ducted vacuum
Alarm system
Surround sound speakers to ceiling
Double Garage
High fences
Security Doors
Rendered Brick House and more
Call me for an inspection and be pleasantly surprised!!!

Description:
Mt Aitken Opportunity
Perfectly located amongst family friendly amenities, this is a rare opportunity to own a beautiful home in the Mt Aitken Estate. Simply move in and enjoy the splendor of this comfortable residence.
This beautiful property is within a short distance to Craigieburn Central, Schools, Parklands, and much, much more. This family home was designed with family living and comfort in mind. It comprises of 3 bedrooms, 2 with BIRs and master boasting a WIR and a ensuite.
The kitchen showcases S/S appliance and ample cupboard space. Complimenting this home is an impressive generous sized family room over looking your low maintenance rear yard.
Additional features include ducted heating, evaporative cooling and single car remote controlled garage equipped with internal access
A truly remarkable home that needs to be inspected to be appreciated. Avoid disappointment and inspect today!!

Description:
6 Gauja Street, Craigieburn - North Facing Brand New Home
(Please use Apple Iphone maps or www.whereis.com to find the address)
Ticks all the buyer's wish list
1. 4 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, 2 Living Areas & double garage
2. 5 Mins drive to Craigieburn Central Shopping Centre
3. Plus, if you're a first home buyer, you may be eligible for the $10,000 FHOG!!
Only 5% to secure the property and balance on settlement!!
Mike Sarupria presents 6 Gauja Street, Craigieburn built by Porter Davis in the prestigious Highlands estate & only a short drive to Craigieburn Central Shopping Centre, Highlands Shopping Centre & schools.
This brand new home comes equipped with luxury turn-key inclusions such as professionally styled interior colour themes, stone bench tops, carpets, tiles, higher ceilings and much more. Front landscaping, driveway and quality flooring are also all included in this beautiful home.
6 Gauja Street Features:
- 4 spacious bedrooms, master will full double vanity ensuite and walk in robe remaining 3 bedrooms with built in robes.
- Well-equipped kitchen & stainless steel cooking appliances including 900 mm gas cook top, range hood, dishwasher, walk in pantry and island bench.
- Open plan living space comprising spacious dining and living area adjacent kitchen.
- Modern central bathroom.
- Spacious laundry
- Central ducted heating and provision for evaporative cooling
- Concrete perimeter around the house and security alarm
- Remote control double car garage and much more!
Call Mike on 0430 126 491 or Frank on 0426 425 361 now for further information or to arrange an inspection.
Photo ID must be presented upon all open & private inspections.
